OL,7,FAn eagle-eyed winner has claimed a
OL,8,Ffree bottle of wine after a company
OL,9,Fhid the offer at the bottom of their
OL,10,Fwebsite's privacy policy - in a bid to
OL,11,Ftest if anyone actually reads them.
OL,13,FTax Policy Associates added the
OL,14,Fpromise to its site's terms and
OL,15,Fconditions in February to test how
OL,16,Flong it would take someone to spot it.
