OL,7,FThe clause read: "This website uses
OL,8,Fcookies so it remembers your name if
OL,9,Fyou leave a comment. You can reject
OL,10,Fthem if you like. We will send a good
OL,11,Fbottle of wine to the first person to
OL,12,Fread this."
OL,14,FFounder Dan Neidle announced on
OL,15,FThursday the offer of a bottle had
OL,16,Ffinally been redeemed three months
OL,17,Flater.
