OL,7,FIn a post on X he said: "Our ongoing
OL,8,Fexperiment into whether anyone reads
OL,9,Fwebsite T&Cs continues. We put this in
OL,10,Four terms back in February. Just got
OL,11,Fclaimed.
OL,13,F"Crazier still is that we're legally
OL,14,Frequired to have a privacy policy,
OL,15,Feven though nobody cares or reads it,"
OL,16,Fhe added.
OL,18,FAccording to the , individuals have a
OL,19,Fright to know if companies collect and
OL,20,Fuse their data.
