OL,7,FAs part of these rules, companies
OL,8,Fholding people's personal data must
OL,9,Fhave a privacy policy on their website.
OL,11,FTax Policy Associates' policy has
OL,12,Fsince been : "We know nobody reads
OL,13,Fthis, because we added in February
OL,14,Fthat we'd send a bottle of good wine
OL,15,Fto the first person to contact us, and
OL,16,Fit was only in May that we got a
OL,17,Fresponse."
